And that's a provable fact?

23:16.220 --> 23:18.353
Yeah. How could thousands
of songs and poems

23:18.355 --> 23:20.087
be about something
that doesn't exist?

23:20.089 --> 23:22.524
Boy, please!
Words on paper.

23:22.526 --> 23:23.892
What would convince you?

23:23.894 --> 23:25.460
If you can't use the
scientific method on it,

23:25.462 --> 23:26.994
then it's not real.

23:26.996 --> 23:28.696
Anything in this world
that's a fact,

23:28.698 --> 23:31.098
it's a fact because we can
either observe it,

23:31.100 --> 23:33.234
measure it,
or experiment with it.

23:33.236 --> 23:34.434
If you can't do
any of those things,

23:34.436 --> 23:37.505
then it's legit,
deadass not real.

23:37.507 --> 23:40.008
But you gotta admit
people are feeling something.

23:40.010 --> 23:42.609
Hormones.
They're feeling hormones.

23:42.611 --> 23:43.912
And we just call it love,

23:43.914 --> 23:46.480
so that we have something
grand to live for.

23:46.482 --> 23:48.516
Otherwise, life seems
really mundane

23:48.518 --> 23:51.118
and just a random
series of events

23:51.120 --> 23:54.591
that you have no control over
until you die.

23:57.994 --> 23:59.861
Depressing, right?

23:59.863 --> 24:02.029
You make it sound depressing.

24:02.031 --> 24:03.567
Because it is.

24:04.868 --> 24:09.205
So, no magic, no fate,
no "meant to be"?

24:10.205 --> 24:11.606
What if I told you
I could get you,

24:11.608 --> 24:16.076
to fall in love with me?
Scientifically.

24:16.078 --> 24:18.212
How is that humanly possible?

24:18.214 --> 24:19.980
Just give me a day.

24:19.982 --> 24:21.682
One day.

24:21.684 --> 24:22.919
Today.

24:24.655 --> 24:27.888
I can't. I don't have a day.

24:27.890 --> 24:29.459
Do you have an hour?

24:39.836 --> 24:41.105
An hour.

24:43.138 --> 24:46.007
I'm not changing
my mind, though.

24:46.009 --> 24:48.542
<i>♪ Life is good, who's askin'? ♪</i>

24:48.544 --> 24:51.846
<i>♪ Wrote my number down
On too many napkins ♪</i>

24:51.848 --> 24:55.316
<i>♪ Got tired of,
"We'll see what happens" ♪</i>

24:55.318 --> 24:58.321
<i>♪ Lights, camera
She 'bout that action ♪</i>

24:59.322 --> 25:01.489
<i>♪ Life is good, who's askin'? ♪</i>

25:01.491 --> 25:05.095
<i>♪ You are not entitled
