34:29.757 --> 34:32.092
I pledge allegiance

34:32.094 --> 34:36.395
to the flag of
the United States of America

34:36.397 --> 34:38.197
<i>and to the Republic...</i>

34:38.199 --> 34:39.766
<i>"Have you ever
been involved</i>

34:39.768 --> 34:41.601
<i>"in anti-government
activities?"</i>

34:41.603 --> 34:43.136
Protect kids not guns!

34:43.138 --> 34:44.774
Protect kids not guns!

34:46.242 --> 34:48.978
<i>"What does America
mean to you?"</i>

34:55.583 --> 34:58.118
Flip your hair a little bit.

35:32.021 --> 35:34.120
We've had a lot of cases
like yours recently.

35:34.122 --> 35:35.890
I think Mr. Martinez
may be able

35:35.892 --> 35:37.993
to help you reopen your case.

35:38.627 --> 35:40.127
Honestly?

35:40.129 --> 35:42.296
I can't make any promises,
especially these days.

35:42.298 --> 35:45.267
But be back 4:30 sharp.

36:04.886 --> 36:06.720
- Hey, Tash.
- Oh!

36:06.722 --> 36:09.823
Hey. Doing nicknames now?

36:09.825 --> 36:12.658
Yeah. How'd your thing go?

36:12.660 --> 36:15.595
Uh... I have to come back
at 4:30.

36:15.597 --> 36:17.932
I guess that just
gives you four hours

36:17.934 --> 36:21.234
to just hang out with me or...

36:21.236 --> 36:25.272
I mean,
I should still go home.

36:25.274 --> 36:27.607
Okay, yeah, how long
does that take?

36:27.609 --> 36:30.044
45, 50ish minutes?

36:30.046 --> 36:31.312
One way?

36:31.314 --> 36:32.578
Yeah.

36:32.580 --> 36:34.548
That's like two hours.

36:34.550 --> 36:37.718
Just to be home
then turn around?

36:37.720 --> 36:39.754
Okay, you make
some fair points.

36:39.756 --> 36:41.024
Yeah.

36:41.557 --> 36:43.124
So?

36:43.126 --> 36:48.298
I have, uh, this thing uptown.
My parents.

36:49.631 --> 36:50.997
- Your parents?
- Yeah.

36:50.999 --> 36:52.133
I just gotta
drop something off.

36:52.135 --> 36:55.336
It's not a big deal at all.

36:55.338 --> 36:58.638
Do you wanna come?

36:58.640 --> 37:02.378
<i>♪ She said she wanna be
My main girl, aye ♪</i>

37:05.548 --> 37:08.750
<i>♪ She said she wanna be
My wife, aye ♪</i>

37:08.752 --> 37:12.252
<i>♪ She think ready
For this life, yeah, yeah ♪</i>

37:12.254 --> 37:15.791
<i>♪ You really think you ready
