37:19.495 --> 37:21.261
- I'm sorry.
- For what?

37:21.263 --> 37:24.031
I'm sorry this isn't exactly
the sexiest first date.

37:24.033 --> 37:25.598
Never agreed it was a date.

37:25.600 --> 37:28.201
Oh, it is. You'll see.

37:28.203 --> 37:30.872
I wish I could just bottle
your confidence and sell it.

37:30.874 --> 37:32.772
'Cause I'd make
a shit ton of money.

37:32.774 --> 37:34.542
I'm not that confident.

37:34.544 --> 37:35.912
Okay.

