Your family,

37:52.361 --> 37:56.596
the South Korean immigrants,
own a black hair care store?

37:56.598 --> 37:57.932
Yes.

37:57.934 --> 37:59.834
My family
of South Korean immigrants

37:59.836 --> 38:03.270
do own a black hair
care store.

38:03.272 --> 38:05.171
Passion project?

38:05.173 --> 38:08.210
It seems random, but it's not.

