<i>See, in the 60s,</i>

38:12.515 --> 38:15.484
<i>wigs made from South Korean
hair were extremely popular.</i>

38:18.486 --> 38:20.220
<i>Around that time,</i>

38:20.222 --> 38:22.756
<i>the South Korean government
banned the export of hair,</i>

38:22.758 --> 38:24.390
<i>making it difficult for anyone</i>

38:24.392 --> 38:27.129
<i>other than Koreans
to make wigs.</i>

38:28.231 --> 38:29.796
<i>Then the U.S. government</i>

38:29.798 --> 38:31.765
<i>banned wigs
made from Chinese hair.</i>

38:31.767 --> 38:36.169
<i>This gave Koreans full control
over the entire wig industry</i>

38:36.171 --> 38:38.571
<i>and the wig business evolved
