38:38.573 --> 38:40.441
<i>black hair care business.</i>

38:40.443 --> 38:45.479
<i>Which, South Koreans
currently control 60 to 80%.</i>

38:45.481 --> 38:49.283
Aisle one is shampoos,
conditioners, dyes,

38:49.285 --> 38:51.484
a bunch of other things
that I don't understand.

38:51.486 --> 38:55.390
Aisle three is weaves,
uh, wigs...

38:56.292 --> 38:58.024
Wow.

38:58.026 --> 39:00.127
This place is huge.

39:00.129 --> 39:02.964
Uh, can I get you anything?

39:02.966 --> 39:05.265
I think I'm set on gel,
but thanks.

39:05.267 --> 39:06.600
No. No!

39:06.602 --> 39:09.136
Uh, I didn't mean a product.

39:09.138 --> 39:10.736
Uh, my dad's got a fridge
in the back

39:10.738 --> 39:12.339
with like soda and...

39:12.341 --> 39:14.375
Mmm, got it. Okay.

39:14.377 --> 39:15.676
Yeah. Thanks.

39:15.678 --> 39:17.380
- A soda would be great.
- Mmm-hmm.

39:29.258 --> 39:31.390
Pink?

39:31.392 --> 39:32.292
Why not?

39:32.294 --> 39:33.961
Doesn't seem like your style.

39:33.963 --> 39:36.430
You never know
what might work.

39:36.432 --> 39:37.433
Hmm.

39:38.267 --> 39:39.566
Mmm-hmm.

39:39.568 --> 39:42.269
I think you'd look beautiful
with a giant, pink afro.

39:42.271 --> 39:45.571
Well, not the whole
thing, just the ends.

39:45.573 --> 39:48.174
- Cool.
- Yeah.

39:48.176 --> 39:49.843
Your hair looks really soft.

39:49.845 --> 39:51.879
You think it can take
all that dye?

39:51.881 --> 39:55.048
Well, you're the black hair
care expert.

39:55.050 --> 39:57.850
So, why don't you feel it
and tell me?

39:57.852 --> 39:59.120
Really?

39:59.122 --> 40:01.857
It's a one-time-only offer.

40:11.334 --> 40:13.267
Aw! What's going on here?

40:13.269 --> 40:14.571
Uh...

40:15.203 --> 40:16.770
Oh, God.

40:16.772 --> 40:18.772
This is my older brother,
Charlie.

40:18.774 --> 40:20.741
This is my friend, Natasha.

